The many competing Anunnaki, Drakonian and Reptilian family lines of the Anu-Melchizedek Leviathan races were a product of progressive Fallen Angelic raiding of an Emerald Covenant hybridization program that began in 155,000 BC. The Founders’ Emerald Covenant hybridization program was intended to assist the Anunnaki and Drakonian/Reptilian races that had joined the Emerald Covenant to regenerate their DNA Templates to reclaim the potentialities of ascension. Genetic engineering was used to combine portions of the Angelic Human DNA Template with that of a composite Anunnaki- Drakonian-Reptilian genetic strain, using the Anunnaki slave-primate Lulcus 5 DNA, upgrading the Neanderthal first to the Luhari, 6 then to the E- Luhli-Levi, 7 E-Luhli-Judah, 8 and E-Luhli-Nephi. 9 After thousands of years of evolution on Earth, and 5 genetic upgrades, the E-Luhli-Levi Cro- Magnon received its final upgrade to the Homo-sapiens-1 Annu- Melchizedek.
